  section
    h4.ui-header-secondary Features
    ul
      li.
        #[strong Lightweight]: the core files are less than #[code.ui-color-emphasis 20 KB] after minifying and gzip compression.
      li.
        #[strong Scalable UI]: all the layout and typography are well-designed using #[code.ui-color-emphasis rem] and #[code.ui-color-emphasis em] units.
      li.
        #[strong Pure CSS Components]: accordion, carousel, dropdown menus, full pages, tooltips, modals.
      li.
        #[strong SVG Icons]: generated by JavaScript and can be easily customized and extended.
      li.
        #[strong Minimal MVC]: declarative views, DOM-based templating, two-way data binding.
